results.deck: Bugbear Entertainment is a Finnish based company located in Helsinki. The company was founded in March 2000 and has since then done games including Rally Trophy, Tough Trucks, Glimerati and the award winning Flatout series. Also the creator of Ridge Racer Unbounded.
results.description:
List of titles created by Bugbear Entertainment:

(2001) Rally Trophy

(2003) Tough Trucks

(2004) FlatOut

(2005) Glimmerati

(2006) FlatOut 2

(2007) FlatOut: Ultimate Carnage

(2007) Sega Rally Revo (PSP game only)

(2008) FlatOut: Head On

(2012) Ridge Racer Unbounded
